nd Sodin. As for the positive\ndirection, in Appendix~B, we prove that the Extended Courant property is true\nfor the isotropic quantum harmonic oscillator in $\\mathbb{R}^2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Jun 2019 16:43:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Jun 2019 21:07:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 11 Mar 2020 18:08:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-04"}
