uingly similar to high $T_c$ cuprates, giving important guideline to\nengineer unconventional superconductivity in oxide heterostructure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 2019 06:28:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-15"}
