e parameters: as the deformation or temperature increases the\nphase transition is suppressed and the disconnected phase is more favored.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 2019 10:50:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 04:00:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 31 Jan 2020 08:05:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-03"}
